data.title: Contact info
data.text:
Embassy opening hours and drop-in consular service:

Monday-Thursday 10:00 am - 12:00 pm and Friday 10:30 am - 12:30 pm

The drop-in consular service includes (service for Swedish citizens): (Swedish passport, ID and driverâ€™s license pick up, life certificates, legalisations, coordination number applications, general questions etc) Please note that migration related issues will not be excepted during these time slots (ie. ID checks, visa/permit application questions).

Schedule a passport appointment: Passports - Sweden Abroad

Please schedule your passport appointment through the above link, available appointments may be scheduled until October 31, 2024. If no appointments are visible in the above link, we are unfortunately fully booked and we kindly ask you to check back at a later date.

Questions about passport services: ambassaden.washington-pass@gov.se

In case of an emergency outside regular office hours, call the Embassy and follow the instructions.

Questions about migration: visa.washington@gov.se Phone hours for specific migration questions is available on Mondays and Wednesdays between 1:30 - 2:30 pm. Please call 202-467-2694.
